# Hacking an Android device remotely using Metasploit

In this hack, we'll be hacking into the android devices like mobiles and tablets by sending them a fake app and installing that `app_name.apk` app on victims phone.
As we know the newer versions of android block this unauthorised app until and unless the victim turn on the `install from unknownsource` option in his security settings. 
But I guess your victim will not be that dumb! unless and untill he's you friend... XD

First we have to find the android exploits and android payloads which are available in metasploit.
